---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="SnapAtlas Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of service for SnapAtlas and North Shore Apps."
>
  <section class="container-custom pt-14 pb-16 md:pt-20">
    <p class="section-kicker">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Last updated: 2026-07-21</p>

    <div class="card mt-8 space-y-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Agreement</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          By using SnapAtlas or this website, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Permitted use</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          You may use SnapAtlas for lawful personal or business photo organization. You are responsible for ensuring
          that your use complies with local laws and data rights obligations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">No warranty</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          SnapAtlas is provided on an as-is basis. While we aim for reliability, we do not guarantee uninterrupted
          availability or suitability for every workflow.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          To the maximum extent allowed by law, North Shore Apps is not liable for indirect or consequential damages
          resulting from use of SnapAtlas.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Terms questions can be sent to <a href="mailto:support@northshoreapps.com" class="text-teal-800 font-semibold">support@northshoreapps.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
